headline: LOS OLIVOS Gritan 'malditos' a asesinos de estudiante
subheadline: Alquilaban mototaxi para cometer sus fechorías bajo la modalidad del 'raqueteo'
author: NA
content: Residents in Los Olivos shout insults at the murderers of a student. The criminals used a mototaxi to commit their crimes under the guise of 'raqueteo.'

headline: CERCADO DE LIMA Chapan a 'Borrado' por robar banco
author: NA
content: A man named 'Borrado' was caught for robbing a bank, while another individual, 'July,' was on his way to assault a gas station.

headline: CARABAYLLO Atrapan a manosos
subheadline: La noche del 13 de febrero, Ayuray Núñez y José Ramírez localizaron a una víctima y se llevaron su celular.
author: "NA"
content: "On February 13th, Ayuray Núñez and José Ramírez targeted a victim in Carabayllo, stealing their phone."

headline: Los venezolanos caen por muerte de policía
subheadline: Un peligroso grupo de la banda Los Papelones de Carabayllo fue detenido cuando iba a asaltar un grifo en Callao.
author: "NA"
content: "A dangerous group from the Los Papelones gang in Carabayllo was arrested for planning to rob a gas station in Callao, following the death of a police officer."
